Unfortunately, there is evidence that this data analysis, despite the many data,
Not always producing the best results. That’s not because a company like multi-health systems doesn’t know how to use data.
Even the data of the most experienced companies are sometimes wrong.
Even Google sometimes makes mistakes.
In 2009, Google announced that by analyzing data, they can predict outbreaks of flu, the bad kind -- by data analysis of Google searches.
